# reflect00 — |00> 반사 (2|00><00|−I = diag(1,-1,-1,-1) = Z⊗Z 후 CZ)
```python id=bloq
from qualtran import BloqBuilder
from qualtran.bloqs.basic_gates import ZGate, CZ
bb = BloqBuilder()
q0 = bb.add_register("q0", 1); q1 = bb.add_register("q1", 1)
q0 = bb.add(ZGate(), q=q0); q1 = bb.add(ZGate(), q=q1)
q0, q1 = bb.add(CZ(), q1=q0, q2=q1)
bloq = bb.finalize(q0=q0, q1=q1)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
golden = np.diag([1, -1, -1, -1]).astype(complex)
```
